Package: doubletree
Type: Package
Title: Causal Estimation with Interpretable Trees
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Denis Agniel
Maintainer: Denis Agniel <dagniel@rand.org>
Authors@R: person("Denis", "Agniel", email = "dagniel@rand.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements methods for causal inference using efficient influence
    function-based estimation with interpretable tree-based models. This package
    builds on optimaltrees to provide doubly robust causal estimation with
    cross-fitting and tree-based machine learning methods.
